snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard - Security Guards Testimony
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s divorce took an unexpected turn after Heard alleged that she had been assaulted by Depp.  Depp’s security guards were on site during the time of the alleged assault, but since they are on Depp’s payroll, how useful will their testimony be? We look into the allegations further with child protection and national security consultant Francey Hakes in this Crime Time highlight hosted by Allison Hope Weiner. 

Watch the full episode here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uLf82la3iY0&index=1&list=PLjk3H0GXhhGfIvJXM3emqDXkZ02SXgfgT
